contentrichtext.text: '''Temu''' can refer to a number of things: * Temu was the evening form of [[Ra]], an ancient [[Ancient Egypt|Egyptian]] god * Temu is a [[Chagga]] Clan Name in [[Tanzania]] * [[Temu (plant)]] is a plant used by aboriginal [[Chile]]ans for medicinal purposes * [[TemÃ¹]] is a commune in the [[province of Brescia]] * Temu, an underground oven used in [[Tonga]]. * Temu, a word in the [[Urhobo language]] meaning a substance or Person reaching a position or status. {{disambig}}
